{"tid":2233982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重提］自抗爭爆發以嚟，香港每700人就有1人曾在抗爭被捕，我哋可以做嘅7件事","createTime":"2020-10-07T13:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:21:09.000Z","uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da86cc34a5b0bde70612fdf3829c59e310309d39","tid":2233982,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:52:35.000Z","msg":"以下摘自黃之鋒facebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3300595316699620/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F3300595316699620%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=a1e11de8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/3300595316699620/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#無選舉無議席唔代表無野做【香港每700人就有1人曾在抗爭被捕，我們可以做的7件事】<br />\n<br />\n足本5分鐘Vlog：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/41230821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F41230821&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=965a2393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/41230821</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n<br />\n不論是撰文分析十二位港人在中國大陸被捕的情況（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363/3290718727687279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fphotos%2Fa.564294826996363%2F3290718727687279&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=0704e5be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363/3290718727687279</a>），抑或是昨天提及反送中以來有接近一萬人被捕（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.313299448762570/3296715687087583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fphotos%2Fa.313299448762570%2F3296715687087583&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ebdcaee2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.313299448762570/3296715687087583</a>） ，很多朋友都關心在國安法通過、武漢肺炎肆虐、政權封殺選舉及街頭示威之下，我們應該如何延續抗爭，與一眾手足同行。<br />\n<br />\n正如我先前的一週報告提到「無議席無選舉唔等於無野做」，我想在抗爭步入新階段的當下，儘管我們無法像過往單靠依賴街頭和選舉發力，但不論是鎂光燈下的政治人物，還是寂寂無名的手足，在過去一年已經開拓各種壯實民主陣營的戰線，可以做的事情實在仍有很多：<br />\n<br />\n一、法庭旁聽聲援<br />\n<br />\n在跟進被捕資訊上，「被捕人士關注組」可謂坊間最為完善的Telegram頻道。除了每日更新審訊情況，更有搜證、送車等副頻道，務求不止報道法庭聆訊消息，更有可能還被控手足一個清白。各位在家工作期間，如能抽出時間旁聽、送車，甚至是協助文字紀錄和收集資訊，必定是對被捕手足最大的支持：<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=da8dd809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a> <br />\n<br />\n二、寫信予在囚手足<br />\n<br />\n作為曾經入獄服刑的過來人，我十分明白身陷囹圄的手足其實很擔心與外間脫節。目前除了依賴議員探監跟進個案、或是營運「解悶工廠」將源源不絕的資訊送入牆內，其實每個人都能寫信予手足，如有餘力，更能與固定手足成為筆友：<a href=\"https://fb.com/bottleshiukachun/posts/1316633175189330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fbottleshiukachun%2Fposts%2F1316633175189330&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=0c059594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/bottleshiukachun/posts/1316633175189330</a> <br />\n<br />\n三、支持黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n過去民間有不少黃店APP，如終極黃藍地圖以及和你PAY等等，衣食住行總有一款合用。飲食以外的行業和服務，譬如保險、清潔、維修、甚至驗樓都有黃色店家，大家不忘一併留意：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157659827906134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157659827906134&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=e117c7bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157659827906134</a><br />\n<br />\n又例如油尖旺區議員協助的「 上善若水 」計劃，已經發展出支援有需要人士的「消費券」，甚或「工作配對」平台等功能，可見只要有人支持，黃色經濟圈就能由消費拓展到生產端，生生不息：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=a4e79fe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n四、參與業委會、法團、社區關注組、支援區議員<br />\n<br />\n去年11月區議會大捷，我們定必要善用得來不易的成果，將民主陣營拓展到社區。由工程圍標、工友權益、社區大白象到全民檢測，不妨聯絡你當區的區議員，總會有你的身位，最低限度，當然是Like曬你所屬行政區的區議員Facebook Page啦！<br />\n<br />\n五、反染紅滲透<br />\n<br />\n正如過往我亦有評論CCTVB斷章取義，為中共取消選舉塗脂抹粉 (<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363/3249448378480981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fphotos%2Fa.564294826996363%2F3249448378480981&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f83a63a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/photos/a.564294826996363/3249448378480981</a>)，連登網民亦有追擊CCTVB，甚至成立「抵制TVB戰線」，呼籲大家罷買和以「派嬲」方式表達對廣告商的不滿，為改變媒體生態而努力：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno4tvb&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=6555b414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/sayno4tvb</a><br />\n<br />\n對於仍然在學或是關注教育議題的朋友，過往積極籌備罷課的前眾志副主席鄭家朗 Isaac Cheng亦有成立新組織教育野 Education Breakthrough ，關注染紅教育、教科書審查等問題，由調查教材到聯署行動都產出不少，歡迎大家一齊推行動做文宣：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/EducationBreakthroughHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEducationBreakthroughHK%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=b9f8a300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/EducationBreakthroughHK/</a> <br />\n<br />\n六、Twitter每日任務<br />\n由攬炒巴遇襲、羅冠聰 Nathan Law流亡以致政權以國安法拘控多名港人，國際戰線絕對是中共的心頭大患。面對中共以銀彈外宣加上民族主義小粉紅洗版，我們更加要動員民間力量，向國際社會傳達警暴真相，呼籲各國支持香港人捍衛民主自由。如果Telegram仍未關注Twitter Channel（<a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=7dc51e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>），希望各位可以加入Twitter戰線，讓世界看見香港。<br />\n<br />\n七、調整心態，繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n總結一句，儘管政權打壓越來越強，街頭抗爭成本日益增加，但沒有正面交鋒的場面不代表抗爭已經完結。相反，抗爭更應結合我們的日常生活。觀乎近日全民檢測、健康碼等議題，政權都正在進化，企圖透過網絡大數據滲透職場、校園等領域，全面監控社會。故此，面對國安法新時代，我們應該同樣要在民間與政權爭持，繼續開拓不同陣線，建立更加鞏固的民間組織，方能反擊政權打壓。<br />\n<br />\n．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．<br />\n💪支持我向世界展現香港人頑強抵抗的意志：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fjoshuawonghk&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=7a3c433c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/joshuawonghk</a><br />\n．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．<br />\n#存亡號召 #絕處逢生 <br />\n✍️<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/joshuawong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fjoshuawong&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ff20a4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/joshuawong</a><br />\n🌐<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=627af89f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf</a><br />\n📷<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/joshua1013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjoshua1013&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=adf233f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/joshua1013</a><br />\n📧joshua@joshuawongcf.com<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TKAE86p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTKAE86p.jpg&h=b7db7a60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89610566311ca420e7a1dc4f8973475c5b8b8cee","tid":2233982,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1dc424af1d6491b41697d9ca7a54fd6c886e7589","tid":2233982,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"601ac9e358c88aaf64b37ffe18d58ddc21b6b3b7","tid":2233982,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3d2c808f1beb248ca0f490f8d11bc26600904a7","tid":2233982,"uid":358691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}